= SDL_SetCursor =
Use this function to set the active cursor.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_SetCursor(SDL_Cursor* cursor)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''cursor'''
|a cursor to make active; see [[#Remarks|Remarks]] for details
|}

